description.narrative: Improve the living conditions of populations in the areas covered by the Sarajevo Water and Waste Water Company and in downstream riverside communities by: (a) reducing the population's exposure to, and reliance on highly polluted water from the Miljacka and Bosna Rivers; and (b) improving the efficiency of the waste water collection network in the Sarajevo Canton.
